  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "account exec",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>We are seeking a skilled and meticulous Accountant to join our team. The ideal candidate will be proficient in managing accounts using Autocount/Xero software, have excellent skills in Microsoft Excel, and be effective in a multilingual work environment. This is a full-time position with a 5.5-day work week (Monday to Saturday).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Key Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage and maintain full sets of accounts.</li>\n  <li>Prepare, verify, and submit e-invoices via the government portal.</li>\n  <li>Perform daily data entry, bookkeeping, and bank reconciliations.</li>\n  <li>Generate monthly financial reports and schedules.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with suppliers, clients, and internal operations teams.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with standard accounting principles.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Qualifications and Skills:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree in Finance, Accounting, or a related field.</li>\n  <li>Minimum of 2 years of hands-on accounting experience.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Autocount/Xero accounting software.</li>\n  <li>Advanced  knowledge of Microsoft Excel (PivotTables, VLOOKUP, formulas, data analysis etc.)</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills in English and Chinese (both verbal and written) – mandatory.</li>\n  <li>Experience with e-invoice submission is a strong advantage.</li>\n  <li>Detail-oriented, independent, and able to meet deadlines.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Willing to work on a 5.5 day week schedule (Monday to Saturday).</p>",
